</div> 
<p><strong>Ancient Dragons' Lightning Spear</strong> is an <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Incantations" href="/Incantations" target="">Incantation</a> in <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Wiki" href="/Elden+Ring+Wiki">Elden Ring</a>. <strong>Ancient Dragons' Lightning Spear spell</strong>&nbsp;summons a red lightning spear&nbsp;to stab enemies from above. Updated to&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Patch Notes" href="/Patch+Notes">Patch 1.07</a>.</p> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<div class="lineleft"> 
 <p><em>A secret incantation of the capital's ancient dragon cult.</em></p> 
 <p><em>Creates a spear of red lightning and stabs it into the ground from</em><br><em>above. On impact, the spear will burst into trails of lightning</em><br><em>covering the area.</em></p> 
 <p><em>Spoken of in legend, red lightning is the weapon wielded by the</em><br><em>ancient dragons.</em></p> 
</div> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Where to find Ancient Dragons' Lightning Spear</h3> 
<p>Where to find <strong>Ancient Dragons' Lightning Spear</strong>:</p> 
<ul> 
 <li>Purchase from <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Brother Corhyn" href="/Brother+Corhyn" target="">Brother Corhyn</a> or&nbsp;<a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Miriel Pastor of Vows" href="/Miriel+Pastor+of+Vows">Miriel, Pastor of Vows</a> after giving the <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Ancient Dragon Prayerbook" href="/Ancient+Dragon+Prayerbook" target="">Ancient Dragon Prayerbook</a></li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
<h3 class="bonfire">Elden Ring&nbsp;Ancient Dragons' Lightning Spear Guide</h3> 
<ul> 
 <li>Stamina Cost: 31</li> 
 <li>One of the <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Dragon Cult Incantations" href="/Dragon+Cult+Incantations">Dragon Cult Incantations</a>&nbsp;and is boosted by the <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Gravel Stone Seal" href="/Gravel+Stone+Seal">Gravel Stone Seal</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;</li> 
 <li>Deals lightning damage</li> 
 <li>Received a poise boost, which gives it hyper armor during the cast.&nbsp;</li> 
 <li>This spell is a close ranged AOE, with many lightning waves spreading out, dealing damage.</li> 
 <li>A single hit of this spell will out perform a single hit of Fortissax's Lightning Spear, but the latter spell hits two total times, and has a much higher Damage/FP cost ratio in total.&nbsp;&nbsp;</li> 
 <li><span style="color: #ff9900;"><em>Note:</em></span> In <a class="wiki_link" title="Elden Ring Patch Notes" href="/Patch+Notes">Patch 1.07</a>, FP cost was reduced from 30 to 25 and the amount of stamina damage done to guarding enemies was increased.</li> 
</ul> 
<p>&nbsp;</p> 
